已完成 FX-032：在 [recharge.ts](C:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/payinces/server/src/routes/recharge.ts:101) 的 `paymentDetails.paymentAttempt` 中记录当前网关订单号及 `superseded` 历史；repay 生成带唯一尝试后缀的新网关单并返回 `previousPaymentLinkInvalidated`，回调及主动验单只接受当前尝试，旧尝试回调记录警告并拒绝入账。守卫已补至 [test-recharge-state-transitions.ts](C:/Users/Administrator/Desktop/payinces/server/scripts/test-recharge-state-transitions.ts:92)。`server type-check`、`test:recharge-state-transitions`、`test:recharge-accounting-guards` 均通过。未改 `package.json`、未 commit。局限：网关仍可能接受旧链接付款，真正取消 Heleket/Antom/易支付旧单需后续 **FX-DISC（网关侧 cancel 集成）**。
